text: Ronald Schröer (born 28 September 1984) is a Dutch long distance runner. Schröer represents Netherlands at international competitions. Schröer is multipe times Dutch national champion. He participates at European Athletics Championships since 2012 in 10,000 metres or the marathon event. He competed at the 2022 European Athletics Championships in the marathon event. ==References== Category:1984 births Category:Dutch long-distance runners Category:Sportspeople from North Holland Category:Living people
